The reward for information leading to a missing 21-year-old West Chester University has reached $50,000.

Shane Montgomery, a senior at the suburban school, was last seen getting kicked out of Kildare's bar in the Manayunk neighborhood of Philadelphia around 2am November 28 and hasn't been seen since.

His mother, Karen Montgomery, announced the latest increase in the reward on Saturday as she turned to NFL fans for help in the search.

